This paper deals with the capacity of MISO fading channels, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the impact of spatial and temporal memory on the fading number, which is related to networking (cs.NI) and signal processing (cs.SI). The paper also mentions beam-forming, which is a technique used in wireless communication (cs.MM) and communication engineering (cs.CE).
